{"pid":"b92ba6da9c791acaf5c0bf5e038e78db91f83310","tid":1468426,"uid":35364,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T19:22:56.000Z","msg":"捉到共狗又唔想就咁放走，<br />\n用幽默手法嘲諷羞辱就夠，<br />\n貼住「平反六四」罰坐，<br />\n破壞證件、報名參軍之類，<br />\n顯得有文化又收威嚇之用。<br />\n<br />\n懲罰並唔一定要流血，<br />\n有時只需要取其象徵意義。<br />\n檯底點懲治黑警都無所謂，<br />\n但檯面一定要好好睇睇。<br />\n<br />\n【反省與建議】「俘虜」處置提案<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1468537\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1468537</a>"},{"pid":"d8552ed8604e2e466e5cb21ae3202bb1141ad557","tid":1468426,"uid":30697,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T19:25:22.000Z","msg":"#我係禮貌撚<br />\n#我係道歉撚 #代香港政府道歉 #要抗爭 撳錢就得<br />\n<br />\n[幫推]<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1468330/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1468330/page/1</a><br />\n&quot;對唔住呀，我地個政府好撚衰，我代佢道歉&quot;<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1467893/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1467893/page/1</a><br />\n對政府不合作 唔係對市民不合作<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n全球道歉運動! <br />\n推到去&quot;民間記者會&quot;.<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1467782/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1467782/page/1</a><br />\n<br />\nSay 句 Sorry, 好易啫 ~ <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n#團結! Be water! Be humble! 香港人有禮貌!<br />\n#816轉美元!<br />\n#612 721 805 811 812<br />\n#和理非勇武！團結d好無！<br />\n#絕不割蓆，唯要改進"},{"pid":"cab7dc00077332b9179d75a958b120b5f1e16216","tid":1468426,"uid":46014,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13